      "description": "Ready to hit the road without breaking the bank? This fair-condition vehicle offers solid, dependable transportation at a price that makes sense! It runs well and handles everyday driving reliably, though it does show some visible wear \u2014 think minor dents, surface scratches, and an interior that reflects its years of use. If you're looking for a practical, honest ride with plenty of life left in it, this could be your perfect match!",
